# OOP Exam – Python (Orders System)

A clean, testable implementation of the exam spec: customers, orders (Regular/VIP), items, favorites auto-update, and gifts — with OOP best practices.

## Requirements
- Python 3.10+ (tested on 3.10/3.11)
- (Optional) venv for isolation

## Setup & Run
```bash
python -m venv .venv
# Windows:
.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
# macOS/Linux:
# source .venv/bin/activate

python main.py



src/
  enums.py            # PaymentType, CustomerType
  gifts.py            # Gift (ABC), CouponGift (prints exact message)
  repositories.py     # OrdersRepository, CustomersRepository (+ reset())
  order_item.py       # OrderItem (repr, validations)
  customer.py         # Customer (favorites mgmt, gift ops, repr)
  order.py            # Abstract Order: common fields, total calc, favorites update
  regular_order.py    # RegularOrder: total = sum(items)
  vip_order.py        # VipOrder: VIP-only + discount
main.py               # Test runner: PASS/FAIL per requirement group
